  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/fb472483d024101ae4a691dc16e9df13.avif?t=1724077533\" width=400 height=300 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/8e3d7c6085b24639d599fecf5a4c04cb.poster.avif?t=1724077533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/8e3d7c6085b24639d599fecf5a4c04cb.webm?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/8e3d7c6085b24639d599fecf5a4c04cb.mp4?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Toilet Paper, please! you are a Toilet Paper Roll who wants to collect all the pieces of toilet paper in the world.<br><br>Face more than 100 levels in this challenging game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/c4accbc6db332ba6baf3e08c18984ddf.poster.avif?t=1724077533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/c4accbc6db332ba6baf3e08c18984ddf.webm?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/c4accbc6db332ba6baf3e08c18984ddf.mp4?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Actually, there is no so much to say, to complete the game you have to collect every single piece of toilet paper in the level<br>before the time runs out, and without getting hit by the dangerous poops and obstacles around the level.<br><br>Use all the powerups you can to defeat the pooh or to restore your health<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/f33d033fa2e92421750ab54e496563ae.poster.avif?t=1724077533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/f33d033fa2e92421750ab54e496563ae.webm?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/f33d033fa2e92421750ab54e496563ae.mp4?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And last, but not least, destroy all the Big Bosses you will find at the end of each world. <br>There are seven of them, and they are pretty angry!<br><br>What are you waiting for?<br><br>Let your journey in the bathrooms around the world begins!<br><br>You can do it! I know you can, and you know it too<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/149030ec0b478dff83199f013ff6d883.poster.avif?t=1724077533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/149030ec0b478dff83199f013ff6d883.webm?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/149030ec0b478dff83199f013ff6d883.mp4?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The game features:<br> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>-105 Levels<br></li><li>- 7 different worlds<br></li><li>- a lot of different powerups<br></li><li>- 7 Final bosses</li></ul></strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/2cd4093504efa7a81e8b26d8239a1646.poster.avif?t=1724077533\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/2cd4093504efa7a81e8b26d8239a1646.webm?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813440/extras/2cd4093504efa7a81e8b26d8239a1646.mp4?t=1724077533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
